Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}每个人都染上了  名为勇气的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:15.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}向着无边无际的梦想天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:19.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}描绘一座通往未来的彩虹桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}共鸣愈发强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}奇迹接连绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:28.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,1200)\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}出发吧！向着明天  闪耀吧  缤纷的旋律
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}是的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}我们绝不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:32.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\3c&H72BFF6&\1a&HFF&}大家的心永远紧紧相连
